fields.title: About Us!
fields.content:
Welcome to the about us page!

This site is designed in a way to be the only site you need for UK ice hockey news.

The most exciting part of this is the player tracker, want to know if your favourite player from last season is going to re-sign for you or if they've signed elsewhere? This is the site for you!

We also have our regularly updated blog to keep you up to date with goings on around the league, there is also a forum for you to join in the discussion.

If you find any bugs please follow our issue tracker to see if it's already been reported and upvote it, if it hasn't been reported yet then please fill in the form to report it.

Find something missing from the site? Then request a feature! We aim to please, we pledge that we will spend at least 50% of our time on building the most voted for feature. To upvote a feature we therefore request you sign up for our monthly subscription.

fields.title: Contact Us!
fields.content:
Welcome to the contact page!

We can be contacted in a variety of ways:

Facebook

Twitter

Email

We also are active on the forum so if it's a minor issue or could start a friendly debate start a thread in 'The Bar' section of the forum.
